Daniel Shechtman Wins 2011 Nobel Prize in Chemistry

-- B y   T o b y   A l d e r
-- 
2011-10-05T09:50:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/daniel-shechtman-wins-2011-nobel-prize-in-chemistry.html
Daniel Shechtman of  Israel  won the 
2011  Nobel Prize  in Chemistry the Royal Swedish Academy of 
Sciences said in a statement today in  Stockholm .  The laureate wins the 10-million Swedish kronor ($1.46
million) prize, the Academy said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Toby Alder at 
 talder@bloomberg.net  